snippet.title: Flora & Fang Guardians of the vampire garden - Game trailer 2
snippet.description:
Flora & Fang: Guardians of teh vampire garden is a one or two player, couch co-op game in the style of arcade adventure classics like Bubble Bobble, Rod Land and Snow Bros.
